rows.label: qst006501_msg0001
rows.name:
A Kujinraman Cookie? For me? But
I'm not really in the mood.

rows.label: qst006501_msg0003
rows.name:
If I don't get my treasure
back... I don't feel like
eating anything...

rows.label: qst006501_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, thank you! I think Janiki went
towards Loska's Great Hole...

rows.label: qst006501_msg1001
rows.name:
You'll get my treasure
back from Janiki, right?

rows.label: qst006501_msg1002
rows.name:
I think Janiki went towards
Loska's Great Hole...

rows.label: qst006501_msg2002
rows.name:
Now I can eat my Kujinraman
Cookie without any worries!

rows.label: qst006501_msg3001
rows.name:
When I grow up, I want my wife
to be someone who can make
delicious Kujinraman Cookies.
